&lt;p&gt;London North West Healthcare NHS Trust is currently expanding the Bank Service. We are now looking to recruit experienced, flexible and reliable Staff Nurses to help play a key role in providing flexible cover within our Trust.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Applicants should be self-motivated, responsible, and empathetic to the individual needs of patients and be able to demonstrate a high level of commitment to patient care. You must also possess excellent communication skills and be open to new ideas and ways of working. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;If you are a NMC registered Staff Nurse wishing to work flexible hours in one of the largest NHS Trusts in the UK, this could be the perfect role for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;LNWH-tr.tssrecruitment@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
